text: A small but Very beautiful art gallery before heading up to ION Sky. Free to visit. Lovely paintings were there for the Myanmar Heritage exhibition.

Free to visit art exhibition. Photography was allowed for the exhibition I visited. The art was well layed out, leaving plenty of space between each piece of work so it did no feel crammed in. I would recommend visiting if you happen to be in ION.
